        <span class="property-indicator"></span>
        <span class="property-type">String</span>
    </dt>
    <dd><p>Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the IAM Role CloudFormation assumes when sending error logging information to CloudWatch Logs.</p>
</dd></dl>
</pulumi-choosable>
</div>
